{"type":"info-page","slug":"mic/papbysection.dtl","journal":"mic","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/mic/papbysection.dtl","title":"Microbiology -- (section view)","bodyHtml":"<a name=\"TOC\" id=\"TOC\"></a>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"></a>\n        <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\">\n        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#000000\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <br>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <p><font size=\"+2\"><strong>Microbiology:</strong></font> <strong>Last updated June 3, 2010</strong> <a href=\"/mic/papbyrecent.dtl\"><nobr>[View by date]</nobr></a></p>\n  <p>Below is a list of all papers that are currently in press (i.e. accepted, awaiting processing or awaiting proofing) for publication. <b>Please note that the abstracts and PDFs are derived from authors' accepted manuscripts and that titles and content are liable to change during preparation for publication.</b> For information on our policy on author self-archiving of this content, please click <a href=\"/mic/misc/self_archiving.dtl\">here</a>.<br>\n  <br>\n  These papers may be cited in the following form:<br>\n  <br>\n  <b>Wasim, M., Bible, A. N., Xie, Z. &amp; Alexandre, G. (2009)</b>. Alkyl hydroperoxide reductase has a role in oxidative stress resistance and in modulating changes in cell-surface properties in <i>Azospirillum brasilense</i> Sp245. Microbiology (in press). doi:10.1099/mic.0.022541-0</p>\n  <p><strong><font color=\"#A70716\">Receive updates by email:</font></strong> <a href=\"/mic/subscriptions/etoc.shtml\">[Sign up for eTOCs]</a></p>\n  <p><strong><a href=\"#PHYSIOLOGY_AND_BIOCHEMISTRY\"> PHYSIOLOGY AND BIOCHEMISTRY</a></strong><br>\n  <strong><a href=\"#CELL_AND_MOLECULAR_BIOLOGY_OF_MICROBES\"> CELL AND MOLECULAR